ext","url":"/docs/Tools#day-0-准备工作","content":"安装 grafana 和 netdata 用于监测服务器运行状态 以及给领导展示；"},"181":{"id":"/docs/Tools-39","page_id":"/docs/Tools","type":"text","url":"/docs/Tools#day-1-热身赛","content":"热身赛通常使用至少一道可以反复提交爆破的题目，引导选手大量提交，测试服务器负载情况。"},"182":{"id":"/docs/Tools-40","page_id":"/docs/Tools","type":"text","url":"/docs/Tools#day-2-正式赛","content":"如果需要发气球请提早给气球打气（通常比赛的前一小时气球组会非常忙）"},"183":{"id":"/docs/Tools-41","page_id":"/docs/Tools","type":"text","url":"/docs/Tools#day-2-正式赛","content":"记得给打印机补纸，小票机同理。"},"184":{"id":"/docs/Tools-42","page_id":"/docs/Tools","type":"text","url":"/docs/Tools#day-2-正式赛","content":"// TODO: 滚榜设置"},"185":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"page","content":"排障指南","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug"},"186":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#hydrooj","content":"hydrooj"},"187":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#前端异常","content":"前端异常"},"188":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","content":"进入服务器控制台，使用 pm2 ls 查看当前运行的进程列表。在正常情况下，应当有四个进程在运行，分别是 hydrooj、hydro-sandbox、mongodb 和 caddy。若进程缺失，请 pm2 stop all 后 pm2 del all 再重新运行安装脚本。"},"189":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","content":"检查各个进程是否已经启动（ status 为 online 且 uptime 至少一分钟）"},"190":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","content":"如果 caddy 无法启动，通常是端口被占用或 ~/.hydro/Caddyfile 配置错误，可尝试 cd ~/.hydro && caddy run 查看详情。如果 hydro-sandbox 无法启动，通常是权限不足 / 内核版本过低，使用 pm2 logs hydro-sandbox --lines 100 查看详情。如果 hydrooj 无法启动 / 启动后没有正常运行，请看下方章节。"},"191":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#hydrooj","content":"pm2 stop hydrooj 关闭后直接使用 hydrooj 参数可让 Hydro 在前台运行，便于查看日志。"},"192":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#hydrooj","content":"尝试更新到最新版本，检查是否能正常使用。"},"193":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#hydrooj","content":"cp ~/.hydro/addon.json ~/.hydro/addon.json.bak 备份插件列表。"},"194":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#hydrooj","content":"hydrooj addon list 查看插件列表，并使用 hydrooj addon remove 名称 禁用所有非官方提供的插件（即不含 @hydrooj/ 前缀的插件）"},"195":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#hydrooj","content":"重启检查是否正常运行。"},"196":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#hydrooj","content":"否则按顺序尝试加载刚刚禁用的插件，检查是否出现异常，联系对应插件提供方解决。"},"197":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#前端异常","content":"指前端页面无法加载（持续转圈或是左下角黄色 / 红色错误提示）"},"198":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#前端异常","content":"使用 Ctrl+Shift+Delete 清除浏览器缓存再试。"},"199":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#前端异常","content":"更新 chrome 浏览器至最新版尝试。"},"200":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#前端异常","content":"同上，尝试禁用第三方插件。"},"201":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#前端异常","content":"如果问题仍未解决，打开 F12 开发者控制台，转到 Console (控制台) 标签页，查看是否有报错信息。"},"202":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#前端异常","content":"打开 Network (网络) 标签页，查看是否有请求失败的情况。"},"203":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","ty