ev/Hydro/packages/utils/lib/status 。当 key 为 end 时表示评测任务已经完成，结果确定，Web 端可进行 AC 数计量，登记成绩表等操作。"},"324":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV","type":"page","content":"权限节点","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV"},"325":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV","content":"Hydro 的权限使用位运算处理。例：若某用户具有 PRIV_EDIT_SYSTEM 与 PRIV_SET_PERM 权限，应设置为 (1<<0)|(1<<1) （即 3）"},"326":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV","content":"可以看 代码 中关于此部分的内容。"},"327":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV","content":"扩展阅读：权限结构"},"328":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout","type":"page","content":"数据库结构","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout"},"329":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout#document","content":"document"},"330":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout#documentstatus","content":"document.status"},"331":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout#record","content":"record"},"332":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout#user","content":"user"},"333":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout#oplog","content":"oplog"},"334":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout#blacklist","content":"blacklist"},"335":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout","type":"heading","url":"/docs/H