"page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#cc-彩色编译错误信息","content":"例："},"688":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-53","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#开大程序运行栈空间","content":"2022/8/12 后安装的实例默认已开启无限栈空间，无需手动操作"},"689":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-54","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#开大程序运行栈空间","content":"在很多时候系统默认为程序提供的栈空间并不能满足我们的需求，此时我们需要手动为用户程序提供更大的栈空间。"},"690":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-55","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#开大程序运行栈空间","content":"修改 pm2 中 hydro-sandbox 的启动参数为 ulimit -s unlimited && /usr/bin/hydro-sandbox ："},"691":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-56","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#提高测评精度","content":"禁用 CPU 频率缩放与 Intel 睿频加速技术，防止 CPU 频率波动。"},"692":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-57","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#提高测评精度","content":"禁用内存地址空间随机化，以使得存在内存寻址错误的代码能够得到更多可重复的结果，可以通过在 /etc/sysctl.conf 中添加下面这行并运行 sudo sysctl -p 应用："},"693":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-58","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存计量不准确","content":"在控制面板上出现内容为 You are using cgroup v2 without kernel 5.19+. This could result in inaccurate memory usage measurements. 警告时，意味着当前系统的内存消耗计量存在误差。"},"694":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-59","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存计量不准确","content":"部分 Linux 设备默认使用 cgroup2，而在 5.19 版本前的内核的 cgroup2 中移除了精确计量内存消耗的接口。\n若要获得更精确的内存计量，推荐启用 cgroup v1 (您可以通过检查 /sys/fs/cgroup/memory/memory.memsw.usage_in_bytes 是否存在来验证是否当前系统是否启用了 cgroup v1 )："},"695":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-60","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存计量不准确","content":"以 Ubuntu 的默认引导器 GRUB 2 为例，编辑 /etc/default/grub：\n在其中"},"696":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-61","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存计量不准确","content":"后，加入 `cgroup_enable=memory swapaccount=1 systemd.unified_cgroup_hierarchy=0，变为："},"697":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-62","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存计量不准确","content":"运行以下命令更新 GRUB 2 的配置，然后重新启动。"},"698":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-63","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存控制器未开启","content":"在控制面板上出现内容为 The memory cgroup controller is not enabled. This could result in inaccurate memory usage measurements. 警告时，意味着当前系统并没有开启内存 cgroup 控制器。"},"699":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-64","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存控制器未开启","content":"部分 Linux (如 Raspbian) 并不会默认开启内存 cgroup 控制器，启用内存控制器可以获得更精确的内存限制和计量。"},"700":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-65","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存控制器未开启","content":"以 Raspbian 为例，编辑 /boot/firmware/cmdline.txt (如果不存在则 /boot/cmdline.txt)：\n在末尾添加（注意空格）"},"701":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-66","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存控制器未开启","content":"重启之后检查 /proc/cgroups 确认内存控制器 memory 已开启。"},"702":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","type":"page","content":"插件","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins"},"703":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins#附加组件列表","content":"附加组件列表"},"704":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins#安装","content":"安装"},"705":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins-2","pag