d":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-21","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-hustoj-升级","content":"dataDir: HUSTOJ 中 data 文件夹的位置（这里存储着题目数据等关键信息，需要手动处理）（OJ_DATA）"},"779":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-22","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-hustoj-升级","content":"uploadDir: HUSTOJ 中 上传文件的位置（这里存储着上传的图片和文件等信息，通常为 /home/judge/src/web/upload/）"},"780":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-23","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-hustoj-升级","content":"当脚本运行完成后，请重启 Hydro 实例，会自动完成之后的升级操作。\n迁移后，请使用原 HUSTOJ 的管理员账号登录实例。"},"781":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-24","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-syzoj-升级","content":"SYZOJ 与 HUSTOJ 迁移方法类似，迁移脚本应运行名为 migrateSyzoj 的脚本外，SYZOJ无需 contestType 参数。\n其参数格式如下："},"782":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-25","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-syzoj-升级","content":"host: 数据库地址"},"783":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-26","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-syzoj-升级","content":"port: 数据库端口"},"784":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-27","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-syzoj-升级","content":"name: 数据库名，一般为 syzoj"},"785":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-28","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-syzoj-升级","content":"username&password: 账号密码，若无则填写空字符串"},"786":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-29","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-syzoj-升级","content":"domainId: 迁入的域，默认为 system"},"787":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-30","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-syzoj-升级","content":"dataDir: SYZOJ 中 data 文件夹的位置（这里存储着题目数据等关键信息，需要手动处理）"},"788":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-31","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-syzoj-升级","content":"由于SYZOJ脚本会将原站所有数据迁移，所以运行耗时较长。\n当脚本运行完成后，请重启 Hydro 实例，会自动完成之后的升级操作。\n迁移后，请使用原 SYZOJ 的管理员账号登录实例。"},"789":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-32","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-universaloj-升级","content":"UniversalOJ （常称作UOJ社区版）与前两者迁移方法类似，迁移脚本应运行名为 migrateUniversalOJ 的脚本。"},"790":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-33","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-universaloj-升级","content":"由于其升级过程较为麻烦，安装脚本已提供自动升级服务，如您需要可运行安装脚本一键迁移，手动迁移请在开发群中提问。"},"791":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-34","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-universaloj-升级","content":"由于UniversalOJ脚本会将原站所有数据迁移，所以运行耗时较长。\n当脚本运行完成后，请重启 Hydro 实例，会自动完成之后的升级操作。\n迁移后，请使用原 UniversalOJ 的管理员账号登录实例。"},"792":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-35","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-vijos-升级","content":"迁移会删除当前 Hydro 的所有数据（含用户账户信息）并移入 vj4 的数据。请注意备份相关文件。"},"793":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-36","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-vijos-升级","content":"请先完成 Hydro 的部署并完成对文件服务的配置(setting_file)。在迁移数据之前，请先停止正在运行的 vj4 服务，仅保留其数据库开启。请注意 Hydro 所在的数据库不应和源 vj4 数据库相同。若您使用 vj4-docker ，可更改 docker-compose.yml 将数据库映射至其他本机端口。"},"794":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-37","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-vijos-升级","content":"安装插件后，您应当能够在 控制面板>脚本管理 中找到名为 migrateVijos 的脚本。其参数格式如下："},"795":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-38","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-vijos-升级","content":"host: 数据库地址"},"796":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-39","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-vijos-升级","content":"port: 数据库端口"},"797":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-40","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-vijos-升级","content":"name: 数据库名"},"798":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-41","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-vijos-升级","content":"username&password: 账号密码，若无则填写空字符串"},"799":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-42","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-vijos-升级","content":"vj4-docker 中数据库名为 vj4，无账号密码。"},"800":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-43","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-vijos-升级","content":"当脚本运行完成后，请重启 Hydro 实例，会自动完成之后的升级操作。\n迁移后，请使用原 vj4 的管理员账号登录实例。"},"801":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-44","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-vijos-升级","content":"若您的 vj4 是由 vj2 或 tyvj 升级而来，在迁移完成后请不要卸载该插件，否则可能导致部分用户无法登录。"},"802":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/recaptcha","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/recaptcha","type":"page","content":"recaptcha","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/recaptcha"},"803":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/recaptcha-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/recaptcha","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/recaptcha","content":"我们采用 reCAPTCHA v3 来检验注册者是否是人类，在注册过程中没有看见传统验证码属正常现象。"},"804":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/recaptcha-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/recaptcha","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/recaptcha","content":"前往 https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin/create 创建 reCAPTCHA 密钥。reCAPTCHA 类型请选择“reCAPTCHA 第 3 版”。"},"805":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/recaptcha-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/recaptcha","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/recaptcha","content":"创建成功后将客户端密钥和服务端密钥分别填入系统设置 recaptcha 栏下的 key 和 secret 中，重启 Hydro 后 reCAPTCHA 即可正常工作。"},"806":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/sonic","page_id":"/docs/Hyd